Class: TextBox

TextBox

Text boxes can be used to display text or to input text. For lots of input you should use the HTML GUI.

new TextBox(text)

Creates a new text box.
Parameters:
Name Type Description
text string The default text to display.
Properties:
Name Type Description
text string The current text.
minWidth number The minimum width this box can have. If the text property is empty the box will still maintain this width.
fontSize number The font size of the displayed text.
font string The name of font to use for the displayed text.
drawBG bool Should the background be filled.
bgColor string The background color of the text box in its initial state.
bgFocusColor string The background color of the text box when it has focus.
borderColor string The border color of the text box in its initial state.
borderFocusColor string The border color of the text box when it has focus.
border number Border width.
padTop number The amount of internal padding at the top of the text box.
padLeft number The amount of internal padding at the left of the text box.
padRight number The amount of internal padding at the right of the text box.
padBottom number The amount of internal padding at the bottom of the text box.
editable bool Can users edit the contents of the text box.
clearOnFocus bool Is the contents cleared when the text box is given focus.
Source:
  • brine-dev.js, line 2734

Extends

  • GUIElement

                                                        TextBox

                                                        Text boxes can be used to display text or to input text. For lots of input you should use the HTML GUI.

                                                        new TextBox(text)

                                                        Creates a new text box.
                                                        Parameters:
                                                        Name Type Description
                                                        text string The default text to display.
                                                        Properties:
                                                        Name Type Description
                                                        text string The current text.
                                                        minWidth number The minimum width this box can have. If the text property is empty the box will still maintain this width.
                                                        fontSize number The font size of the displayed text.
                                                        font string The name of font to use for the displayed text.
                                                        drawBG bool Should the background be filled.
                                                        bgColor string The background color of the text box in its initial state.
                                                        bgFocusColor string The background color of the text box when it has focus.
                                                        borderColor string The border color of the text box in its initial state.
                                                        borderFocusColor string The border color of the text box when it has focus.
                                                        border number Border width.
                                                        padTop number The amount of internal padding at the top of the text box.
                                                        padLeft number The amount of internal padding at the left of the text box.
                                                        padRight number The amount of internal padding at the right of the text box.
                                                        padBottom number The amount of internal padding at the bottom of the text box.
                                                        editable bool Can users edit the contents of the text box.
                                                        clearOnFocus bool Is the contents cleared when the text box is given focus.
                                                        Source:
                                                        • brine.js, line 2627

                                                                                                              Array

                                                                                                              TextBox

                                                                                                              Text boxes can be used to display text or to input text. For lots of input you should use the HTML GUI.

                                                                                                              new TextBox(text)

                                                                                                              Creates a new text box.
                                                                                                              Parameters:
                                                                                                              Name Type Description
                                                                                                              text string The default text to display.
                                                                                                              Properties:
                                                                                                              Name Type Description
                                                                                                              text string The current text.
                                                                                                              minWidth number The minimum width this box can have. If the text property is empty the box will still maintain this width.
                                                                                                              fontSize number The font size of the displayed text.
                                                                                                              font string The name of font to use for the displayed text.
                                                                                                              drawBG bool Should the background be filled.
                                                                                                              bgColor string The background color of the text box in its initial state.
                                                                                                              bgFocusColor string The background color of the text box when it has focus.
                                                                                                              borderColor string The border color of the text box in its initial state.
                                                                                                              borderFocusColor string The border color of the text box when it has focus.
                                                                                                              border number Border width.
                                                                                                              padTop number The amount of internal padding at the top of the text box.
                                                                                                              padLeft number The amount of internal padding at the left of the text box.
                                                                                                              padRight number The amount of internal padding at the right of the text box.
                                                                                                              padBottom number The amount of internal padding at the bottom of the text box.
                                                                                                              editable bool Can users edit the contents of the text box.
                                                                                                              clearOnFocus bool Is the contents cleared when the text box is given focus.
                                                                                                              Source:
                                                                                                              • GUI.js, line 203
